Etimirishe enjore e Daudi

(
1   Int 
18  .
1  -
17  )


1  Ore te siadi ena nemir Daudi Ilfilisti neitore ninche, neya Daudi Metegama aitung'uaa enkaina oo Lfilisti.


2  Nemir ninye Moab, netem ninche to lgosoi lkereri, aisho ninche meirraga te nkop; ore ilkererin oare netemi pee eari metuata, ore olkereri obo olulung'a nepali. Neaku Ilmoabu isinkan le Daudi neyaki kodi.


3  Neitoki sii Daudi amir Hadadesa olayioni le Rehob, olaiguanani le Soba, eloito arrinyu enkitoo enye to lkeju le Frati. 
4  Neya Daudi aitung'uaa ninye enkalifu o iip naapishana o sikarini ooked mbartan, oo sikarini nkalifuni tikitam oopuo too nkejek nedung Daudi irrisheta mbartan pooki oo ngarrin, kake etelekua inaaidip ngarrin iip oo mbartan. 
5  Ore ake pee epuonu Isiria le Dameski aaretu Hadadesa ilo aiguanani le Soba, near Daudi metuata iltung'ana nkalifuni tikitam oare loo Siria. 
6  Nepik Daudi iltimito atua Aram e Dameski; neaku Isiria isinkan le Daudi neyaki kodi. Neisho Olaitoriani Daudi metimirisho te pooki wueji neba anaa eneshomo. 
7  Neya Daudi ilong'oi e sahabu apa naanapita isinkan le Hadadesa, neyau ninche Yerusalem. 
8  Ore ebaiki Beta ometabaiki Berotai, nkanas e Hadadesa, neya olaiguanani Daudi isuyan kumok.


9  Ore ake pee ening Toi olaiguanani le Hamat nchere etimira Daudi enjore pooki e Hadadesa, 
10  neirriwaa Toi olayioni lenye Yoram enetii olaiguanani Daudi, pee eisho ninye enchunet, o pee eisho ninye enchunet enkaraki nataarare Hadadesa nemir ninye; amu kesej apa eeta Hadadesa olarrabal o Toi. Neyau Yoram te nebo ninye ntokitin e nkosholai, o sahabu, o no suyai. 
11  Ore sii kuna neitisiny olaiguanani Daudi to Laitoriani, te nebo ina osholai o sahabu apa naaitisinya naaing'uaa iloreren pooki apa ootimira ninye, 
12  ebaiki Edom, o Moab, o Ilamoni, o Ilfilisti, o Amaleki, o naaing'uaa iyarunot e Hadadesa olayioni le Rehob, olaiguanani le Soba.


13  Neishur enkarna e Daudi. Ore pee eshukunye ninye, nesesekuan Iltung'ana nkalifuni tomon o isiet ti atua Oerata le Munyan. 
14  Nepik ninye iltimito Edom; ore atua Edom pooki nepik iltimito, lelo le Edom pooki isinkan le Daudi. Neishoo Olaitoriani Daudi metimirisho te pooki wueji neba anaa eneshomo.


15  Neaku eitoria apa Daudi Israel pooki; neisiaisho Daudi te sipata o te risioroto too ltung'ana lenyena pooki. 
16  Naa Yoab olayioni le Seruiya apa oitore enjore, naa Yehoshafat olayioni le Ahilud apa olaigeroni. 
17  Naa Sadok apa olayioni le Ahitab o Ahimelek olayioni le Abiata ninche ilapolosak; naa Seraia apa olasirani; 
18  naa Benaia olayioni le Yehoida apa otii shumata lelo Kereti o lelo le Peleti ore ilayiok le Daudi naa ilapolosak.

